==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zea
<hw>Ze"a</hw> <pr>(z⟦emac⟧"⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a
kind of grain, fr. Gr. <grk>ze`a</grk>, <grk>zeia`</grk>; cf. Skr.
<ets>yava</ets> barley.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of large
grasses of which the Indian corn (<spn>Zea Mays</spn>) is the only
species known. Its origin is not yet ascertained. See
<er>Maize</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

